components.name: CartUpdateFormComponent
components.templateData:
<form [formGroup]="form" (ngSubmit)="onSubmit()" class="cart-update-form" *transloco="let t; read: 'cartList.item'">
  <ui-input type="number" name="quantity" formControlName="qty"/>
  <ui-button
    [label]="t('updateLabel')"
    [disabled]="!form.dirty"
    size="small"
    type="submit"
    variant="outline"
  />
</form>

components.name: InputComponent
components.templateData:
<input
    [(ngModel)]="value"
    (ngModelChange)="onChange($event)"

  [type]="type"
  [id]="id"
  [name]="name || ''"
  [placeholder]="placeholder"

  [disabled]="disabled"
  [readonly]="readonly || false"
  [required]="required || false"
  [pattern]="pattern || ''"
  [min]="min"
  [max]="max"
  [step]="step"

  [autocomplete]="autocomplete"
  [autofocus]="autofocus"

  class="input"
/>

components.name: LabelComponent
components.templateData:
<label
  [for]="htmlFor"
  class="label">
  <ng-content/>
</label>

components.name: LanguageSelectorComponent
components.templateData:
<ui-button
        *ngFor="let language of langs"
        (onClick)="switch(language)"
        size="small"
        [variant]="activeLanguage === language ? 'secondary' : 'ghost'"
        [label]="language.toUpperCase()"
/>

components.name: RadioButtonGroupComponent
components.templateData:
<fieldset class="container">
  <legend class="sr-only">Size</legend>
    <label *ngFor="let option of options"
      class="btn-label"
           [htmlFor]="'option-'+option.value"
      [class.btn-label-selected]="option.value === value"
      (click)="writeValue(option.value)"
           [attr.tabindex]="0"
      >
      <input
        type="radio"
        [name]="name"
        [id]="'option-'+option.value"
        [value]="option.value"
        [checked]="option.value === value"

        [attr.tabindex]="-1"

        (change)="writeValue(option.value)"
      />
      {{option.label}}
    </label>
</fieldset>
